If thre is no space to build a rail from both ends of the station, but the station is not the end station, Polany station is useful too. Train will enter the station, turn around and then go out the station and continue in the original direction.

Polany station can not be built on a line with a heavy traffic because there can be only one train in each direction, and other trains have to wait before the staition. This can be solved with the waiting bay, but it will not be good anymore. The trains have to slow down when entering or leaving the station too.
